        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="项目安装："><a href="#项目安装：" class="headerlink" title="项目安装："></a>项目安装：</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-node" data-language="node"><code class="language-node">npm init vue<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>选择如下选项：<blockquote><p>typescript<br>pinia<br>vue router<br>jsx<br>Eslint<br>prettier</p></blockquote></li></ul><h3 id="运行："><a href="#运行：" class="headerlink" title="运行："></a>运行：</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-node" data-language="node"><code class="language-node">npm run dev<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
